{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d1e4e8afd2","title":"关于胡、曾、关敌南下及我军部署致周恩来电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"925f88c4e9","index":0,"year":1936,"month":12,"day":23,"articleId":"d1e4e8afd2"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c3e2499b71","type":"paragraph","text":"关于胡、曾、关敌南下及我军部署","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d1e4e8afd2"},{"id":"47d7b75f34","type":"paragraph","text":"致周恩来电","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d1e4e8afd2"},{"id":"401b2a09e0","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年12月23日）周：","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d1e4e8afd2"},{"id":"fa28810220","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、胡、曾、关准备南下，判断不走海静即走固镇，但不会走庆阳。现周、孔”退金积，再向中宁堡，顾祝同到宁夏后尚须与胡、关会商，判断须一星期后才能开始动作。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d1e4e8afd2"},{"id":"1cef7e9d2f","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、提议作如下部署：","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d1e4e8afd2"},{"id":"81fbcaea03","type":"paragraph","text":"一、固原、平凉、西峰、镇原四点东北军位置四个师筑确屯粮，为死守计，必要时固原、西峰再增加一个师，马洪（鸿）宾守黑城镇李旺堡线。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d1e4e8afd2"},{"id":"5952e9d68e","type":"paragraph","text":"二、庆阳、合水由萧劲光占领","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d1e4e8afd2"},{"id":"795790328d","type":"paragraph","text":"三、罗炳辉为司令员，宋时轮为副司令员，宋任穷为政委，指挥二十八军、三十二军、骑一团及二十九军主力，尾敌前进威胁政侧后","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d1e4e8afd2"},{"id":"86bb7ae639","type":"paragraph","text":"四、准备调四方面军向兰州平凉，由兰州补充其被服弹药，如何盼复。","index":8,"publicat